{"id":223,"parent_id":218,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":223,"title":"Judges 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Judg.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Deborah and Barak sing a song of praise because Israel is delivered from Canaanite bondage."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.1","order":"02.08.005.19382"},["b","1"],"Then",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"sang"],"Deborah and Barak the son of Abinoam on that day, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.2","order":"02.08.005.19383"},["b","2"],"Praise ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"for the avenging of Israel, when the people willingly offered themselves."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.3","order":"02.08.005.19384"},["b","3"],"Hear, O ye kings; give ear, O ye princes; I,",["i","even"],"I, will sing unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; I will sing",["i","praise"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.4","order":"02.08.005.19385"},["b","4"],["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", when thou wentest out of Seir, when thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"marchedst"],"out of the field of Edom, the earth trembled, and the heavens dropped, the clouds also dropped water."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.5","order":"02.08.005.19386"},["b","5"],"The mountains",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"melted"],"from before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","even"],"that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Sinai"],"from before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.6","order":"02.08.005.19387"},["b","6"],"In the days of Shamgar the son of Anath, in the days of Jael, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"highways"],"were unoccupied, and the travellers walked through byways."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.7","order":"02.08.005.19388"},["b","7"],["i","The inhabitants of"],"the villages ceased, they ceased in Israel, until that I Deborah arose, that I arose a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"mother"],"in Israel."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.8","order":"02.08.005.19389"},["b","8"],"They chose new",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"gods"],"; then",["i","was"],"war in the gates: was there a shield or spear seen among forty thousand in Israel?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.9","order":"02.08.005.19390"},["b","9"],"My heart",["i","is"],"toward the governors of Israel, that offered themselves willingly among the people. Bless ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.10","order":"02.08.005.19391"},["b","10"],"Speak, ye that ride",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"on white asses"],", ye that sit",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"in judgment"],", and walk by the way."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.11","order":"02.08.005.19392"},["b","11"],["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"They"],"that are delivered"],"from the noise of archers in the places of drawing water, there shall they rehearse the righteous acts of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","even"],"the righteous acts",["i","toward the inhabitants"],"of his villages in Israel: then shall the people of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"go down to the gates."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.12","order":"02.08.005.19393"},["b","12"],"Awake, awake, Deborah: awake, awake, utter a song: arise, Barak, and lead thy captivity captive, thou son of Abinoam."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.13","order":"02.08.005.19394"},["b","13"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Then"],"he made him that remaineth have dominion over the nobles among the people: the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"made me have dominion over the mighty."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.14","order":"02.08.005.19395"},["b","14"],"Out of Ephraim",["i","was there"],"a root of them against Amalek; after thee, Benjamin, among thy people; out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Machir"],"came down governors, and out of Zebulun they that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"handle"],"the pen of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"writer"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.15","order":"02.08.005.19396"},["b","15"],"And the princes of Issachar",["i","were"],"with Deborah; even Issachar, and also Barak: he was sent on foot into the valley. For the divisions of Reuben",["i","there were"],"great thoughts of heart."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.16","order":"02.08.005.19397"},["b","16"],"Why abodest thou among the sheepfolds, to hear the bleatings of the flocks? For the divisions of Reuben",["i","there were"],"great searchings of heart."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.17","order":"02.08.005.19398"},["b","17"],"Gilead abode beyond Jordan: and why did Dan remain in ships? Asher continued on the sea shore, and abode in his breaches."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.18","order":"02.08.005.19399"},["b","18"],"Zebulun and Naphtali",["i","were"],"a people",["i","that"],"jeoparded their lives unto the death in the high places of the field."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.19","order":"02.08.005.19400"},["b","19"],"The kings came",["i","and"],"fought, then fought the kings of Canaan in Taanach by the waters of Megiddo; they took no gain of money."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.20","order":"02.08.005.19401"},["b","20"],"They fought from heaven; the stars in their courses fought against Sisera."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.21","order":"02.08.005.19402"},["b","21"],"The river of Kishon swept them away, that ancient river, the river Kishon. O my soul,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"thou"],"hast trodden down strength."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.22","order":"02.08.005.19403"},["b","22"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Then"],"were the horsehoofs broken by the means of the pransings, the pransings of their mighty ones."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.23","order":"02.08.005.19404"},["b","23"],"Curse ye Meroz, said the angel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", curse ye bitterly the inhabitants thereof; because they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"came"],"not to the help of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to the help of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"against the mighty."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.24","order":"02.08.005.19405"},["b","24"],"Blessed above",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"women"],"shall Jael the wife of Heber the Kenite be, blessed shall she be above women in the tent."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.25","order":"02.08.005.19406"},["b","25"],"He asked water,",["i","and"],"she gave",["i","him"],"milk; she brought forth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"butter"],"in a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"lordly dish"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.26","order":"02.08.005.19407"},["b","26"],"She put her hand to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"nail"],", and her right hand to the workmen’s hammer; and with the hammer she smote Sisera, she smote off his head, when she had pierced and stricken through his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"temples"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.27","order":"02.08.005.19408"},["b","27"],"At her feet he bowed, he fell, he lay down: at her feet he bowed, he fell: where he bowed, there he fell down dead."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.28","order":"02.08.005.19409"},["b","28"],"The mother of Sisera looked out at a window, and cried through the lattice, Why is his chariot",["i","so"],"long in coming? why tarry the wheels of his chariots?"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.29","order":"02.08.005.19410"},["b","29"],"Her wise ladies answered her, yea, she returned answer to herself,"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.30","order":"02.08.005.19411"},["b","30"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"Have"],"they not sped? have they",["i","not"],"divided the prey; to every man a damsel",["i","or"],"two; to Sisera",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"a"],"prey of divers colours, a prey of divers colours of needlework, of divers colours of needlework on both sides,",["i","meet"],"for the necks of",["i","them that take"],"the spoil?"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.31","order":"02.08.005.19412"},["b","31"],"So let all thine enemies perish, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": but",["i","let"],"them that love him",["i","be"],"as the sun when he goeth forth in his might. And the land had rest forty years."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.1a","order":"02.08.005.19413"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/singing"},"TG Singing"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.4a","order":"02.08.005.19415"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.7"},"Ps. 68:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.5a","order":"02.08.005.19417"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"quaked.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/97.5"},"Ps. 97:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/1.4"},"Micah 1:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.9"},"Hel. 12:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/22.10"},"3 Ne. 22:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.74"},"D&C 109:74"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.22.21-22,40"},"133:22 (21–22, 40)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.34"},"Moses 6:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.5b","order":"02.08.005.19419"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.8"},"Ps. 68:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.6a","order":"02.08.005.19421"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.22.21-22"},"Lev. 26:22 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.7a","order":"02.08.005.19423"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-motherhood"},"TG Marriage, Motherhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.8a","order":"02.08.005.19425"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.17"},"Deut. 32:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.10a","order":"02.08.005.19427"},["b","10a"],["span.small","IE"],"on animals used by rich merchants, leaders."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.10b","order":"02.08.005.19429"},["b","10b"],"Hebrew meaning uncertain; perhaps “on rich cloths, carpets.”"],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.11a","order":"02.08.005.19431"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"By the voices of archers down among the watering places, there they rehearse the righteousness of Jehovah, even the righteousness of His rulers in Israel. Then the people of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"went down to the gates."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.13a","order":"02.08.005.19433"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Then a remnant descended against the nobles; the people of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"descended for me against the mighty."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.14a","order":"02.08.005.19435"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/32.40"},"Num. 32:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/17.1"},"Josh. 17:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.14b","order":"02.08.005.19437"},["b","14b"],["span.small","HEB"],"hold the sceptre of the muster-officer, the marshal’s staff."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.14c","order":"02.08.005.19439"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.21a","order":"02.08.005.19441"},["b","21a"],["span.small","HEB"],"(perhaps) tread (them) down with might."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.22a","order":"02.08.005.19443"},["b","22a"],["span.small","OR"],"Then did the horse hooves stamp."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.23a","order":"02.08.005.19445"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/21.5.5-6"},"Judg. 21:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.24a","order":"02.08.005.19447"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.25a","order":"02.08.005.19449"},["b","25a"],["span.small","HEB"],"curds, curdled milk."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.25b","order":"02.08.005.19451"},["b","25b"],["span.small","HEB"],"bowl of nobles."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.26a","order":"02.08.005.19453"},["b","26a"],["span.small","HEB"],"tent peg or pin."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.26b","order":"02.08.005.19455"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/4.21.17-21"},"Judg. 4:21 (17–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.30a","order":"02.08.005.19457"},["b","30a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Are they not finding, dividing spoil?"],["div",{"id":"30b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.30b","order":"02.08.005.19459"},["b","30b"],["span.small","OR"],"a spoil of dyed stuffs."]]}
